Module-3
7. Simulate a program in C for ARM microcontroller using KEIL
to sort the numbers in ascending/descending order using
bubble sort.
#include <lpc214x.h>
// Swap function
void swap(int* arr, int i, int j)
{
int temp = arr[i];
arr[i] = arr[j];
arr[j] = temp;
}
// A function to implement bubble sort
void bubbleSort(int arr[], int n)
{
int i, j;
for (i = 0; i < n - 1; i++)
// Last i elements are already
// in place
for (j = 0; j < n - i - 1; j++)
if (arr[j] > arr[j + 1])
swap(arr, j, j + 1);
}
// Driver code
int main()
{
int arr[] = { 5, 1, 4, 2, 8 };
int N = sizeof(arr) / sizeof(arr[0]);
bubbleSort(arr, N);
return 0;
}
14
8. Simulate a program in C for ARM microcontroller to find
factorial of a number.
#include <lpc214x.h>
// Function to find factorial of a given number
unsigned int factorial(unsigned int n)
{
int result = 1, i;
// loop from 2 to n to get the factorial
for (i = 2; i <= n; i++) {
result *= i;
}
return result;
}
int main()
{
int res,num = 6;
res=factorial(num);
return 0;
}

9. Simulate a program in C for ARM microcontroller to
demonstrate case conversion of characters from upper to
lowercase and lower to uppercase.
upper to lowercase
#include <lpc214x.h>
int main ()
{
char upr[50]="ABCD",lwr[50]; // declare character array
int i = 0;
/* use while loop to iterate the character array string until '\0' not
occur. */
while (upr [i] != '\0')
{
lwr [i] = upr[i] + 32; // Add 32 to string character to convert into lower
case.
i++;
}
return 0;
}
16
lower to uppercase
#include <lpc214x.h>
int main ()
{
char lwr[50]="abcd",upr[50]; // declare character array
int i = 0;
/* use while loop to iterate the character array string until '\0' not occur.
*/
while (lwr [i] != '\0')
{
upr [i] = lwr[i] - 32; // Add 32 to string character to convert into lower
case.
i++;
}
return 0;
}
Module – 4 and 5
10 Demonstrate enabling and disabling of Interrupts in
ARM.
AREA Program,CODE,READONLY
ENTRY
; Enabling IRQ Interrupt
MRS r1,cpsr
BIC r1,r1,#0x80
MSR cpsr_c,r1
; Enabling FIQ Interrupt
MRS r1,cpsr
BIC r1,r1,#0x40
MSR cpsr_c,r1
; Disabling IRQ Interrupt
MRS r1,cpsr
ORR r1,r1,#0x80
MSR cpsr_c,r1
17
; Disabling FIQ Interrupt
MRS r1,cpsr
ORR r1,r1,#0x40
MSR cpsr_c,r1
B1 B B1
END
